Detailed Description

ObitSource class definition.

This class is derived from the Obit class.

This class contains information about a given source.

Usage

Instances can be obtained using the newObitSource constructor, the ObitSourceCopy constructor or a pointer duplicated using the ObitSourceRef macro. When an instance is no longer needed, use the ObitSourceUnref macro to release it.
